These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, iris
City: hamburg, prague
House: victorian, townhouse
1. the victorian house is not to the right of the person who growsiris##8
2. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| Flower          | iris | orchid    |
| City         | prague   | hamburg |
| House   | victorian  | townhouse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
2 different games are played: canasta, chess
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, marigold
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, software-developer
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, december
1. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
2. the person who growslily is somewhere to the left of the librarian##5
3. the software-developer is not to the right of the librarian##8
4. the person who's birthday is in march is not the person who growsmarigold##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Game    | canasta        | chess    |
| Flower       | lily         | marigold |
| Job         | software-developer | librarian   |
| Birthday   | march               | december  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, video-games
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, lilac
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, blend
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
1. the montecristo-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the blend-smoker is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Hobby   | writing       | video-games |
| Color   | black       | lilac    |
| Cigar   | montecristo | blend |
| Pet           | cat        | ferret   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, sudoku
There 2 different types of food: lemon, apple
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, basketball
2 different games are played: go, poker
1. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the person eating apple##5
2. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the left of the person playing poker##8
3. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | sudoku | singing  |
| Food           | apple  | lemon |
| Sport   | basketball | golf   |
| Game     | poker   | go |

