.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-11::.
2 different pets are kept: horse, ferret
There are 2 different nationalities: mexican, pakistani
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, dancing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, dubstep
1. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
2. the mexican is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the fan of r&b is not the owner of the horse##6
4. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the fan of r&b##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Pet   | horse      | ferret |
| Nationality   | mexican    | pakistani   |
| Hobby         | dancing | hiking     |
| Music-Genre     | dubstep | r&b  |

