The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, nurse
City: miami, san-francisco
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse
1. the person traveling to miami is not to the right of the prince-smoker##8
2. the nurse is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |
| Cigar          | prince         | pall-mall    |
| Job           | entrepreneur | nurse   |
| City   | miami   | san-francisco    |
| Sport     | biathlon         | lacrosse |

 